# Restaurant endpoints
### Get all restaurants
GET http://localhost:5193/api/Restaurants
#Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get restaurant by Id
GET http://localhost:5193/api/Restaurants/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Restaurant not found
GET http://localhost:5193/api/Restaurants/2

### Add new restaurant
POST  http://localhost:5193/api/Restaurants
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "Name": "Test Restaurant",
  "Description": "Test Description",
  "Category": "Polish",
  "HasDelivery": true,
  "ContactEmail": "test@test.com",
  "ContactNumber": "123456789",
  "City": "Test City",
  "Street": "Test Street",
  "PostalCode": "22-222"
}

### Delete restaurant
DELETE http://localhost:5193/api/Restaurants/1

### Update restaurant
PATCH http://localhost:5193/api/Restaurants/9
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Name": "Modified name",
  "Description": "Modified description",
  "HasDelivery": true
}

### Create dish
POST http://localhost:5193/api/restaurant/2/dishes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Example Dish",
  "description": "Delicious dish made with fresh ingredients.",
  "price": 2,
  "kiloCalories": 2,
  "restaurantId": 1
}

### Get all dishes for specific restaurant
GET http://localhost:5193/api/restaurant/2/dishes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

